metadata.name: Medici BLeU Fashion Collage
metadata.description:
After generating many AI fashion models, I decided to make a Dada photomontage collage artwork. I transformed my curated fashions into Medici's models using AI generated portraits of the grande patron.

I selected the special bleeding skull that I generated a short time ago. Behind the skull, as a blended background, I placed the famous TJO BleU. Then a couple of diffusion percentages were blended to generate this noisy collage.
